<DOCNO> LA071594-0050 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 060739 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
July 15, 1994, Friday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
